Nergard – 2013–present ===
In 2013, Kravljaca appeared alongside among others Göran Edman, Nils K Rue and Ralf Scheepers as one of the lead vocalists on Norwegian melodic metal band Nergard's first album 'Memorial for a Wish'.
In 2015 the Norwegian band released another album, titled 'A Bit Closer to Heaven' which again featured Kravljaca alongside other vocalists such as Elize Ryd and Nils K. Rue.
